These are Puzzles for 1x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, mexican, malaysian, indian, british
1. the indian is in the middle##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the british##1
3. the malaysian is in an odd position##4
4. the malaysian is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2  |   3   |   4   |  5  |
| Nationality   | malaysian | chinese | indian | mexican | british |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-2::.
House: farmhouse, modern, palace, cape-cod, tower
1. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
2. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
3. the modern house is in an odd position##4
4. the palace house is on the far right##1
5. the modern house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |     3     |     4     |     5      |
| House   | cape-cod | tower | modern | farmhouse | palace |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: sailing, tennis, golf, cycling, basketball
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
3. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |  3   |     4      |   5   |
| Sport   | tennis | golf | sailing | cycling | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, may, september, february, april
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |       1       |     2     |       3        |   4    |     5     |
| Birthday   | february | may | september | april | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-5::.
House: palace, craftsman, futuristic, tower, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the palace house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
4. the craftsman house is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |  2   |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| House   | tower | townhouse | futuristic | craftsman | palace |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-6::.
5 different games are played: bridge, canasta, monopoly, poker, scrabble
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing bridge and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3    |    4     |  5   |
| Game   | bridge | monopoly | poker | canasta | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-7::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, roller, airplane, quad-bike, van
1. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the van##2
2. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |     2      |   3   |    4     |    5    |
| Transport   | bike | airplane | van | roller | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-8::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, pall-mall, cain, chaman, ritmeester
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |  3   |     4     |    5    |
| Cigar   | chaman | cain | ritmeester | davidoff | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-9::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, lily, amaryllis, rose, aconite
1. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
2. the person who growsaconite is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growslily##1
5. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
6. the person who growsiris is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |   2   |   3   |  4   |     5      |
| Flower   | aconite | amaryllis | lily | iris | rose |

