.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-10::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, puzzles, traveling, card-games, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2  |  3   |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby   | puzzles | collecting | card-games | traveling | baking |

