3. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating mango and the person eating artichoke##2
4. the person eating strawberry is in the middle##1
5. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4     |   5    |
| Food   | radish | mango | strawberry | artichoke | grapefruit |

