2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Beverage   | juice | almond-milk | 7up | hot-chocolate | coffee |

