1. the person playing billiard is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing domino##2
2. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing domino is between the person playing billiard and the person playing backgammon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2  |    3     |    4     |   5    |
| Game   | scrabble | billiard | domino | backgammon | chess |

 